nization, the mitochondrial genome of M. recondita was replaced by that of the resident M. gracilis. This study illustrates how apparent signatures of sympatric divergence can arise from complex histories of allopatric divergence, colonization and hybridization, thus highlighting the need for rigorous analyses to distinguish between such scenarios.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Kuo, Hao\u2010Chih", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Chen, Shiang\u2010Fan", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Fang, Yin\u2010Ping", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Cotton, James A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Parker, Joe D.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Csorba, G\u00e1bor", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Lim, Burton K.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Eger, Judith L.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Chen, Chia\u2010Hong", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Chou, Cheng\u2010Han", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Rossiter, Stephen J.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/d842162cd8da4f9fa78082ddd5515852", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/a0822db0a27441cfec5778d57a31a1affd8de313fe4f3884cd533c8d90a45408", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/DJT5FQ67", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/DJT5FQ67", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/87df3c56b8fa7aa704a3326b4f9043bf!/b14863-17317", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"]